{"tid":1256694,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]選舉管理委員會取消晚上區議會選舉活動建議指引公眾諮詢大會","createTime":"2019-06-25T07:07:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-25T10:12:37.000Z","uid":57274,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9c83994421eb9b32be141e4fe3e9f9d80688a866","tid":1256694,"uid":57274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T07:07:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=353081&amp;home=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D353081%26home%3D1&d=DgFN9ivcdgICzBQxXV443g1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=a42fbef8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D353081%26home%3D1&h=0ff55a79\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=353081&amp;home=1</a><br />\n【Now新聞台】選管會經風險評估後，決定取消晚上舉行的區議會選舉活動建議指引公眾諮詢大會。<br />\n<br />\n選管會表示，舉辦公眾諮詢大會邀請市民出席發表意見，要考慮場內所有參與者的安全。基於安全及保安考慮，決定取消諮詢大會。<br />\n<br />\n諮詢大會原訂晚上七時在鰂魚涌社區會堂舉行，選管會主席馮驊出席。<br />\n<br />\n區議會選舉活動指引作出多項修訂建議，包括在提名候選人章節中加入確認書制度，要求參選人簽署聲明，確認擁護基本法及效忠香港特別行政區，有網民發起晚上出席諮詢大會抗議。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">政府好驚驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"4f4d798f3b37ed37d3f6f92f63f5da1643945cc7","tid":1256694,"uid":57274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T07:08:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">各位巴打今晚抖下 <br />\n派下傳單<br />\n留力聽日<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"46685059a5f0dca7fea8c208b7e3162c091c91b0","tid":1256694,"uid":57274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T07:09:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img 